<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">* وَالوَاجِبَاتُ ثَمَانِيَةٌ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>جَمِيعُ التَّكْبِيرَاتِ غَيْرَ تَكْبِيرَةِ الإِحْرَامِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُ:</span> <span class="c2">«سُبْحَانَ رَبِّيَ العَظِيمِ»</span> فِي الرُّكُوعِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُ:</span> <span class="c2">«سَمِعَ اللَّهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ»</span> لِلْإِمَامِ وَالمُنْفَرِدِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُ:</span> <span class="c2">«رَبَّنَا وَلَكَ الحَمْدُ»</span> لِلْكُلِّ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُ:</span> <span class="c2">«سُبْحَانَ رَبِّيَ الأَعْلَى»</span> فِي السُّجُودِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُ:</span> <span class="c2">«رَبِّ اغْفِرْ لِي»</span> بَيْنَ السَّجْدَتَيْنِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَالتَّشَهُّدُ الأَوَّلُ، وَالجُلُوسُ لَهُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>